race.comment: MACARONI MONELLI (2) collided in the run and missed the frame when fifth (22.97) at this track over 400m in a Free For All. Has the ability and looks hard to top. ANOTHER JIMMY (6) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for six wins and three minors. Missed the frame latest (23.33) when seventh over 400m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Makes strong appeal on best. ARTISAN ARTIST (1) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (22.80) at this track in a Grade 4. Can improve sharply here. MY BOY BEAST (3) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.
